      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://grow.amplemarket.com/b2c92ea2044b-affiliate"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting started is straightforward. Head to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Amplemarket's website",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", choose the Startup plan (perfect for small teams), and set up your account. The onboarding includes community sessions where experts walk you through the interface. I configured my first campaign in under 30 minutes – the AI guides you intuitively.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip: Integrate your CRM right away to sync existing contacts. Amplemarket works smoothly with tools like Salesforce, making data flow effortless.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Define Your Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) with AI",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Amplemarket's AI helps you pinpoint the right prospects. Go to the \"Prospecting\" section and input criteria like industry, job title, and company size. The AI then scans its vast database to suggest high-intent leads. For example, when I targeted SaaS CMOs, it surfaced over 500 verified contacts with recent engagement signals.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/amplemarket-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This step saves hours of manual research. Learn more best practices in ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Amplemarket tips",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Generate and Enrich Leads Automatically",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's where Amplemarket shines. With one click, the AI generates a list of prospects, complete with verified emails and phone numbers. It enriches data with social insights, so you know each lead's interests. I used this to build a pipeline of 200 qualified leads in a day – something that used to take me a week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://grow.amplemarket.com/b2c92ea2044b-affiliate"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Ready to dive in? ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Try Amplemarket's prospection now",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see the difference.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Craft Personalized Outreach Sequences",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Amplemarket's outreach tool uses generative AI to draft personalized emails and sequences. You select a template, and the AI tailors messages based on each lead's profile. For instance, it referenced a prospect's recent LinkedIn post in one email, boosting my reply rate by 40%.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Schedule sequences to send automatically, and track opens in real-time. This automation frees you up for closing deals.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Leverage Sales Coaching and Analytics",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform includes an AI coach that analyzes your calls and emails, offering feedback on tone and pacing. After a demo call, it suggested I ask more open-ended questions, which improved my conversion rate. Analytics dashboards show pipeline health and ROI, helping you refine strategies.",
            "marks": []
          }
